ADD GALAXY_VIEW_TITLE:0 "Galaxy View"
CN2 GALAXY_VIEW_TITLE:0 "星系地图"
ADD GALAXY_VIEW_DESC:1 "The galaxy view provides an overview of the galaxy and your Empire within it. It is recommended for most of your interactions."
CN2 GALAXY_VIEW_DESC:1 "星系地图提供了对星系及星系中你的帝国的概览。游戏互动大多推荐使用此地图。"
ADD TUTORIAL_MISSION_VIEW_TITLE:0 "Missions"
CN2 TUTORIAL_MISSION_VIEW_TITLE:0 "任务"
