ADD OUTLINER__SECTORS_TITLE:0 "Sectors"
CN2 OUTLINER__SECTORS_TITLE:0 "星域"
ADD OUTLINER__SECTORS_DESC:0 "Sectors are administrative regions within an Empire, consisting of multiple colonized planets. A sector can be assigned a §SGovernor§! and a §SSector Focus§!, allowing the sector to develop itself automatically towards the given focus, reducing the need for constant management."
CN2 OUTLINER__SECTORS_DESC:0 "星域是帝国内部的行政区域，由多颗殖民星组成。每个星域都可以指派一名§S总督§!并设置§S星域发展重点§!，使星域可以自行按给定的重点发展，减少玩家频繁管理的负担。"
ADD OUTLINER__MILITARY_FLEETS_TITLE:0 "Military Fleets"
CN2 OUTLINER__MILITARY_FLEETS_TITLE:0 "军用舰队"
ADD OUTLINER__MILITARY_FLEETS_DESC:0 "Use the ships in your fleet to defend your Empire, or to conquer enemies."
CN2 OUTLINER__MILITARY_FLEETS_DESC:0 "使用舰队中的舰船来保卫国家，或是征服敌人。"
ADD OUTLINER__CIVILIAN_SHIPS_TITLE:0 "Civilian Ships"
CN2 OUTLINER__CIVILIAN_SHIPS_TITLE:0 "民用舰船"
ADD OUTLINER__CIVILIAN_SHIPS_DESC:0 "Use these ships to survey nearby star systems and build new structures in them."
CN2 OUTLINER__CIVILIAN_SHIPS_DESC:0 "使用这些民用船只调查毗邻的恒星系以及在恒星系内建设新设施。"
ADD RESOURCE_PANEL__EMPIRE_MANAGEMENT_TITLE:0 "Empire Management"
CN2 RESOURCE_PANEL__EMPIRE_MANAGEMENT_TITLE:0 "帝国管理"
ADD RESOURCE_PANEL__EMPIRE_MANAGEMENT_DESC:0 "Large Empires are difficult to manage, so keep an eye on these indicators as your Empire grows."
CN2 RESOURCE_PANEL__EMPIRE_MANAGEMENT_DESC:0 "大型帝国难于管理，所以在发展你的帝国时要对这些指标保持关注。"
ADD RESOURCE_PANEL__FLEET_MANAGEMENT_TITLE:1 "Starbase and Fleet Management"
CN2 RESOURCE_PANEL__FLEET_MANAGEMENT_TITLE:1 "恒星基地及舰队管理"
